# Lotaya Shwe Oh — Production Target

**Primary production hosting: Z.com Private Hosting** (Ubuntu + Nginx + PHP + MySQL on one server).

Render is **temporary testing only** — never design features or architecture around Render limitations.

## Stack (final)

| Component | Location |
|-----------|----------|
| Flutter app | Play Store — points/rewards only, no in-app cash withdraw UI |
| Laravel API | Z.com — `api-laravel/` |
| Exchange website | Same Laravel app — `/exchange` |
| Admin panel | Same Laravel app — `/admin` |
| MySQL | Z.com local MySQL (`127.0.0.1`) — always on |

## When switching hosts

Only change:
- Server `.env` (`APP_URL`, `EXCHANGE_URL`, `DB_*`)
- Flutter `--dart-define=API_URL=...` and `EXCHANGE_URL=...`

Do **not** rewrite Flutter or Laravel business logic.

## Deploy reference

See `deploy/zcom/README.md` for the canonical production deploy guide.
